title: Cowes Regatta
brief_description: Hundreds of craft assemble in the harbour at Cowes, to participate in the world famous regatta. From Cowes the film takes you to the Brittania Cup race, 1965, with the Duke of Edinburgh and Princess Anne competing in the royal yacht, Bloodhound.
